                <h3 class="site-title">James Cropper Paper</h3>

                 <div class="site-text">
                    James Cropper Paper is a custom speciality papermaker and converter, and one of the world’s foremost makers of coloured paper.
                    The business is renowned globally for papers that support industries from luxury packaging to framing and digital imaging.
